menu "breadboard: bb_sink_http"

config BB_SINK_HTTP_RESP_BUF_BYTES
    int "Response buffer size for HTTP publish (bytes)"
    default 256
    help
        Size of the stack-allocated response buffer used by bb_sink_http on
        each publish call. AWS IoT Core returns a minimal JSON body on
        success; 256 bytes is sufficient. Increase if your endpoint returns
        larger responses.

endmenu
